@* A container: it renders whatever content the parent nested inside it (decision 131). It does NOT
   name itself anywhere -- the nesting in NestedSame.razor is the PARENT's markup, which is the whole
   distinction the cycle guard has to get right. *@
<div class="card">@ChildContent</div>

@code {
    [Parameter] public RenderFragment? ChildContent { get; set; }
}
